description: Information on the shipping label of a Snow device that is being returned to Amazon Web Services.

parameters.name: JobId
parameters.description: The automatically generated ID for a job, for example JID123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426655440000.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status information of the task on a Snow device that is being returned to Amazon Web Services.

nested_items.name: ExpirationDate
nested_items.description: The expiration date of the current return shipping label.

nested_items.name: ReturnShippingLabelURI
nested_items.description: The pre-signed Amazon S3 URI used to download the return shipping label.
